From 5020b99bb6c000b2111ab26be1f2f85ebdfdb6b9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: youyx <youxiao@huawei.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 10:26:04 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] [WIP][Store] Add put/get session APIs for ranged
 multi-buffer transfers

Expose batch_put/get_start/end and multi_buffer_ranges so callers can
reserve objects once, transfer object-byte ranges with cached lease/
replica metadata, and finalize without re-querying Master on each range.

Also add abnormal-session UTs (including lease expiry dropping get
sessions) and a real TcpTransport e2e under mooncake-store/tests/e2e.
